Class Contact

java.lang.Object
  eu.etaxonomy.cdm.model.common.CdmBase

          eu.etaxonomy.cdm.model.agent.Contact
All Implemented Interfaces:
ICdmBase, Serializable
public class Contact
extends VersionableEntity

The class for information on how to approach a person or an institution. It includes telecommunication data and an electronic as well as multiple postal addresses.

This class corresponds to:

  • ContactDetails according to the TDWG ontology
  • Contact (partially) according to the ABCD schema

Version:
1.0
Author:
m.doering

public Set<Address> getAddresses()
